Make a Plot

Plot the penguin data with bill length by bill depth

penguins %>% ##using the penguin dataset
  ggplot(aes(x=bill_length_mm, 
             y=bill_depth_mm, 
             color=species)) + 
  geom_point() + 
  geom_smooth(method = "lm") + #add a linear regression 
  labs(x="Bill Length (mm)", 
       y="Bill Depth (mm)", 
       color = "Species") + 
  theme_bw()
